commitResults.messageBody: Echo commands by user and exit when user types 'bye'.
User input is now added to an item list. 'list' command prints the list.
Task class created. User can mark task in list as done.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add Todo, Event and Deadline Tasks
commitResults.messageBody:
Implements TodoTask, EventTask, DeadlineTask classes as subclasses of Task.

Keying in  'done' without anything after no longer causes an error.

Some wrong user inputs are now handled with try-catch blocks instead of if-else blocks.

Some redundant code removed.

runtest.sh can be used to semi-automate testing.

Added delete function to remove tasks from list.

The number of tasks in list will now be printed whenever a new task is added or removed.
